Be Better Hotels helps independent hoteliers to strengthen their business in the digital age of the travel industry, providing them an integrated set of cloud-based tools that allows them to manage their online marketing, reservations and daily operations.

The company brings their clients the access to a technology they would not be able to develop with their own resources, in order to fortify their competitive position in the hotel industry landscape.

With Be Better Hotels' services, hoteliers can: 
a) receive online direct reservations, saving the high commissions they pay to intermediaries 
b) easily build and update self-managed websites, optimizing conversion and saving time and money they pay to web designers
c) manage hotel daily operations with efficiency
d) take strategic decisions based on key performance indicators, avoiding "trial and error" strategy
e) distribute room prices and availability in several online sales channels, saving time and expanding its market reach 
f) monitor guest reviews that affects their online reputation
g) share knowledge and experiences with peers
h) improve skills and learn to execute marketing tactics to increase revenue

12.short_description: Better hearing means better quality of life

18.description:
uSound is the result of extensive research , developed to become the main alternative to the latest generation programmable hearing aids and audio streaming to traditional systems of hearing and normal hearing. Through a combination of technology applied to health , Usound is positioned as an application that goes beyond just playing the sound volume changing environment , it adjusts and optimizes individually each of the frequency of sounds entering the Smartphone , allowing all its features would be aligned to the specific hearing loss of the user , matching the quality of digital hearing aids , today valued in the market at a price ranging from U$D 2000 U$D 5000.

The possibilities Usound gives people with hearing difficulties are great . Initially, a flat rate test allows about your hearing level and calibrate your Smartphone optimally according to their hearing levels and headphone features available to the user . Once your Smartphone is calibrated, you can start playing the audio set to your ear level , if you have a bluetooth headset you can leave your Smartphone nearby to the sound source and located at a distance that allows your headset , getting the sound with the same quality and intensity with which he would receive if close to the sound source.
